{"tid":2098120,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"612 人道支援基金出左週年報告！ 一年總支助金額約7千5百萬","createTime":"2020-07-07T09:05:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T11:09:12.000Z","uid":22556,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"986917f3c7a10ff66ec9784a4d9da9f699b9ac7c","tid":2098120,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T09:05:27.000Z","msg":"【年度工作報告　徵求寄放點】<br />\n　<br />\n＊一週年工作報告連結：<a href=\"https://612fund.hk/s/612-annual-report.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F612fund.hk%2Fs%2F612-annual-report.pdf&d=mNwaOXjJ1pf0GC%2FIettivQp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=955a0e5a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://612fund.hk/s/612-annual-report.pdf</a> ＊<br />\n<br />\n612人道支援基金印製了 2019 - 2020 年度週年工作報告，希望向大家報告基金自去年6月成立後的工作及支援概況，徵求可以協助寄放及派發週年報告的合作夥伴／地點。<br />\n希望各大黃店、議辦或其他各類型場所的朋友協助！<br />\n　<br />\n如能協助，請填寫以下表格，基金稍後會聯絡你確認及安排。將會根據數量，可能安排送貨或郵寄；預算 7月第四週起送到。<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/yV2KkNZCpYWeyoLLA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FyV2KkNZCpYWeyoLLA&d=mNwaOXjJ1pf0GC%2FIettivQp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=1870ec66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/yV2KkNZCpYWeyoLLA</a><br />\n　<br />\n如有查詢，歡迎聯絡基金熱線：Whatsapp/TG 9845 6641<br />\n資料絕對保密，只作今次寄放用途，發放後即會銷毀。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/368482457185258/posts/597819754251526/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F368482457185258%2Fposts%2F597819754251526%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=mNwaOXjJ1pf0GC%2FIettivQp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=2682351b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/368482457185258/posts/597819754251526/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"b994ceaae06d4daa500ea9db85a7b871212e9b7b","tid":2098120,"uid":4574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T09:09:00.000Z","msg":"課金<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8867c2da682aafaf51814b1d597c928905f04dae","tid":2098120,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike"